India Power’s Rural Electrification Planning $500 Million in Franc Bonds

-- B y   A n u r a g   J o s h i
-- 
2011-05-02T07:51:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/rural-electrification-plans-500-million-swiss-franc-yen-bonds.html
Rural Electrification Corp.,  India ’s
state-controlled lender to power projects, plans to sell as much
as $500 million of Swiss franc and yen-denominated bonds,
Finance Director Hari Das Khunteta said in an interview today.  Rural Electrification has sought approval from the  Reserve
Bank of India  and the power ministry to sell debt, Khunteta
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anurag Joshi in Mumbai at 
